description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Anurak purrs with a rating of 69, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 138, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, Leverage for East, 3 for South, and Box for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/20692-76343-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [138 Votes, Top 15% Score]
